   "body" : "This reworks/revives https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/15848 to add a check for low disk space on first startup and issue a warning if disk space is below the expected space required to accommodate the blocks.\r\n\r\nNote we extracted a few constants just within init.cpp, but they could be applied more generally if there is a better place for them.\r\n\r\nThis PR was fashioned by a team of developers at the [bitcoin++](https://www.btcplusplus.dev/) conference workshop: \"[Let's contribute to Bitcoin Core](https://sched.co/12P6Z)\"\r\n\r\nFixes #15813",
